      "weather": "Fine",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "END OF ERA (1) is first up since finishing eighth (21.75) in a Grade 5 at this track over 352m four-and-a-half months ago. Solid record at the distance winning six races. Well placed here and will can go close with a clear run. BIG ZEAL (8) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 1.3 lengths win at Q Parklands in a handy 30.29. Draws out wide but in form and has the ability. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from six attempts. Must be included in calculations. RUXTON SPICE (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (20.64) in a Mix 5 at this track. Won at her only start from this draw. Can do much better this time. PANAMA POWER (4) is in form and worth thought again.",
